{"tid":2436381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台工會真係完美演繹乜撚嘢叫做欺善怕惡","createTime":"2021-03-07T06:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T07:46:06.000Z","uid":83906,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97936fc9456209b7ef596f4726cff0faad65dbfe","tid":2436381,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"一開始梁家榮上台嘅時候就係你班友仔屌佢係共產黨<br />\n點知人哋企得仲硬過你<br />\n人哋上立法會幫你擋箭擋到成個心口都係窿<br />\n你哋個濕鳩公會就淨係識捉住佢嚟屌<br />\n唔幫手都算啦仲要拖後腿<br />\n最後就被俾你哋因為BBC單嘢屌到心灰意冷提早退休<br />\n新嗰個一上場就DQ節目 <br />\n然後你哋就啞撚咗咁樣 一句聲都唔敢出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利君雅單嘢仲撚搞笑 佢俾人搞你哋淨係出乜撚嘢快閃示威<br />\n對住鏡頭say個hi都叫做做咗嘢咁不如send電郵算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88b83681f5ec6b26c9bb51e05e2823155a18c3c","tid":2436381,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff9ef8eff7e51dfadc080916b25d203a556cb1b","tid":2436381,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e5ca566d596f388173682035dae13b35bb9af8","tid":2436381,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae7985ab79265820378800c0f88dc11c5c6f5a2","tid":2436381,"uid":83906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4f7